Representational State Transfer/REST is a web standard based architecture that uses HTTP Protocol for data communication
The most commonly used methods:
GET
PUT
DELETE
POST

command to copy warfile to tomcat
clean install war:war org.codehaus.mojo:wagon-maven-plugin:upload-single -Dwagon.fromFile=<war-path> -Dwagon.url=file://<tomcat-webapps-path>

